Package com.geodesk.feature.store

Class AnonymousWayNode

java.lang.Object
com.geodesk.feature.store.AnonymousWayNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Feature, Node
public class AnonymousWayNode extends Object implements Node
A Node without tags that doesn't belong to a Relation, i.e. one that isn't a proper feature, but merely defines the geometry of a Way.
